                        <p>Alternative contact options:</p>
                        <div class="alt-buttons">
                            <a href="https://mail.google.com/mail/?view=cm&fs=1&to=derekdevon17@gmail.com" target="_blank" class="alt-btn">
                                <i class="fas fa-envelope"></i> Open in Gmail
